sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Gateway as KServe Gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant REST as OVMS REST Server<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant gRPC as OVMS gRPC Server<br/>9178/TCP gRPC
    participant Handler as HttpRestApiHandler
    participant MP as MediaPipe Graph<br/>Calculator
    participant SM as ServableManager
    participant OV as OpenVINO Runtime
    participant Cloud as Cloud Storage<br/>(S3/GCS/Azure)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant HF as HuggingFace Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over Client,HF: Flow 1: REST Inference (OpenAI-compatible v3 API)
    Client->>Gateway: POST /v3/chat/completions<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    Gateway->>REST: Forward (HTTP 8080)<br/>API Key (optional)
    REST->>Handler: Drogon routes request
    Handler->>MP: Execute MediaPipe Graph
    MP->>OV: LLM Calculator inference<br/>Continuous batching
    OV-->>MP: Token generation
    MP-->>Handler: Response / SSE stream
    Handler-->>REST: JSON / SSE response
    REST-->>Gateway: HTTP Response
    Gateway-->>Client: Chat completion response

    Note over Client,HF: Flow 2: gRPC Inference (KServe v2)
    Client->>gRPC: ModelInfer RPC<br/>9178/TCP plaintext
    gRPC->>SM: KFSInferenceServiceImpl
    SM->>OV: Model Instance inference
    OV-->>SM: Inference result
    SM-->>gRPC: InferResponse
    gRPC-->>Client: gRPC Response

    Note over Client,HF: Flow 3: Model Loading from Cloud Storage
    SM->>Cloud: HTTPS GET model artifacts<br/>TLS 1.2+, Cloud credentials
    Cloud-->>SM: Model files (IR, ONNX, etc.)
    SM->>OV: Load model into runtime

    Note over Client,HF: Flow 4: HuggingFace Model Pull
    SM->>HF: HTTPS git clone/pull<br/>TLS 1.2+, HF_TOKEN (optional)
    HF-->>SM: Model repository files
    SM->>OV: Load pulled model
